name: yes i am precious
description:
yes i am precious is the result of my first solo game jam! i made it to remind u of something that seems like common sense... that u are SOOOOO precious... that no matter what anyone says about u or even what u believe about yourself u can't forget those three words. don't let those creatures fool u ~

 I worked on yes i am precious from nov. 8-9 , 2014 at the nyu game center. ^__^

* music is an 8-bit version of hillsong's relentless

* all the art and code by me, jenny jiao hsia (@q_dork) 

* special thanks to alec thomson (@alecthomson)
